Take a look at [this blog post|https://confluence.atlassian.com/confcloud/blog/2017/06/edit-attached-files-with-the-apps-on-your-desktop] for all the details.

Looking for similar functionality for Confluence Server? Check out KontextWork's awesome [GoEdit add-on|https://marketplace.atlassian.com/plugins/de.kontextwork.goedit/server/overview] on the Atlassian Marketplace.
