In Confluence, we have the option to configure different [Scheduled Jobs|https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/DOC/Scheduled+Jobs] so the instance will do some procedures "automatically". 

This is a feature request to have as bundled, an option to schedule a space import based on a file that you can use for Confluence. In example, I have the Space XML for the space that I would like to import in Confluence, then, by only using this file and scheduling a time, Confluence will automatically import it.

