Confluence has the JIRA Chart Macro built in, which allows for the display of JIRA chart data without the need of adding an external JIRA gadget into Confluence once an Application Link has been established.

The original JIRA Pie Chart gadget allows users to click slices of the pie, which takes users to the JIRA Issue Navigator showing the relevant issues that make up that slice. However, the new JIRA Chart Macro is not interactive. It would be nice to have this built in to reach feature parity.

